	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et vitae innocentiam a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeter meritum expostulaveram tecum proximis litteris<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Oben <ref target="file#11296">Nr. 1253</ref>, 2-7.</note> super diuturno silentio tuo, <persName ref="154">Myconi</persName> charissime.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pulchre enim missis interim litteris<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Oben <ref target="file#11295">Nr. 1252</ref>.</note> resarcisti, quod quaerebar deesse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">De caesareanis insidiis seu proditionibus<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. ebd., Z. 3-21.</note> nihil dubito.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominum oro, ut virum sanguinem et bella volentem<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist Kaiser <persName ref="1332">Karl</persName> V.</note> opprimat ad gloriam nominis sui.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si Anglus<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="98">König <persName ref="98">Heinrich VIII.</persName></persName></note> in foedus christianum receptus est<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file#11291">Nr. 1248</ref>, 9-11 mit Anm. 8.</note>, fac sciam.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostri mercatores huius nihil retulere.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Illi res suas agunt.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil quaestionis aut curae illis est de religione aut periculis evangelio imminentibus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich hoff alls<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">immer.</note>, wölle ye der keysser dem bapst imm arß stecken<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Vgl. oben <ref target="file#11295">Nr. 1252</ref>, 21 mit Anm. 11.</note>, er werde ze letst drinn ersticken.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quamvis perpetuo me terreat nostra ingratitudo, perversitas, ambitio, luxus nimius vitaque impoenitens.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed „non nobis, domine, sed nomini tuo da gloriam, ne dicant gentes: Ubi est deus eorum<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Ps 115, 1f (113, 9f Vulg.).</note>.“</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus hoc ardentius, quaseo, et vigilemus, quo vehementius isti nobis malum parant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName ref="118">Cellario</persName><note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="118">Diethelm Keller</persName>; vgl. oben <ref target="file#11295">Nr. 1252</ref>, 22-24.</note> nihildum scriptum novi.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro tua diligentia gratias tibi ago.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="84">Rodolphus</persName><note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="84">Rudolf Gwalther</persName>.</note> meus non potest satis praedicare tuam beneficentiam et humanitatem<note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12">Vgl. oben <ref target="file#11275">Nr. 1232</ref>, 12-15.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus sit merces tua.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iuvabis illum porro haud dubie, quemadmodum hactenus parentis et tutoris loco fuisti.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam reciperetur a d. <persName ref="81">Grynaeo</persName><note xml:id="fn13" type="footnote" n="13">Vgl. oben <ref target="file#11295">Nr. 1252</ref>, 25-32.</note>; non quod apud te male illi prospectum sit, sed quod volentem et benevolum te<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">te <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> non gravo impudenter neque onero libenter.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="81">Grynaeus</persName> rebus ecclesiasticis minus occupatus est te.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi apud nos nihil habemus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Faxit dominus, ut non infausta habeamus brevi non ab uno loco.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et me ama.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">18. aprilis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="84">Rodolphum</persName>, Buttlerum<note xml:id="fn14" type="footnote" n="14"><persName ref="37">John Butler</persName> ist der Überbringer dieses Briefs; vgl. unten <ref target="file#11302">Nr. 1259</ref>, 4.</note> et Ryfenstein amato; nam te ex animo colunt.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Anno 1539.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus tuus ut semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="154">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, antistiti clarissimo <placeName ref="97">Basileiensis</placeName> ecclesiae, charissimo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
